com.interpss.simu.multicase.datatype
Interface SwingVoltageUpdateRec

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IEMF<Bus,Branch>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
SwingVoltageUpdateRecImpl
public interface SwingVoltageUpdateRec
extends IEMF<Bus,Branch>

A representation of the model object 'Swing Voltage Update Rec'. Data record to update a swing bus. It is used in the multi-net Loadflow algorithm.

The following features are supported:

  • Remote Node Id
  • Aclf Net Id
  • Aclf Net Name
  • Swing Bus Id
  • VMag
  • VAng
